attributionInfo.brokerName: Keller Williams Realty Boston-Metro | Back Bay

description: This recently renovated single-family home in South Boston features 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and a private roof deck with stunning city views. The interior boasts hardwood flooring throughout and a spacious, open-concept layout ideal for modern living. The kitchen includes stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and contemporary cabinetry. The home offers central heating, updated bathrooms, and great natural light. Located in a vibrant South Boston neighborhood, it's close to popular restaurants, cafes, fitness studios, and new developments.
